        <mxCell id="FEvFGn3x2a5UFLXiZ1Df-14" parent="1" style="strokeWidth=1;shadow=0;dashed=0;align=center;html=1;shape=mxgraph.mockup.text.stickyNote2;fontColor=#666666;mainText=;fontSize=17;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#ffffcc;strokeColor=#F62E00;" value="- This model is not keeping the track of historic data which means that we do not record the status before updating it. I assume it works because in the business model, it&#39;s clear how the status changes and they are limited so we can imply the history of the changes. Or we don&#39;t care about the past, and we only care about the current situation." vertex="1">
